      "content": "it doesnt feel like just \"brain chemistry\" though. it feels more fundamental. like my actual foundation is different. i was reading about how high-energy cosmic rays during solar flares can actually trigger epigenetic changes or even localized mutations. i feel like i was exposed to something intense a few months ago and my dna actually got updated or something. can science actually explain a rapid cognitive leap like that?",
